===========================================================================
    The package is serial function of ALLIS.
    It's include tcp server tcp_client udp client/server and test function.
    Use Select design.
===========================================================================    
auto_send       It's random auto send "A-Z" "a-z" "0-9" data by console.
                Baudrate 57600.
                Example :  auto_send /dev/ttyUSB0 .

client          It's test function Tcp client and print message from tcp server.
                Example : client server_ip server_port . 

server          It's test function Tcp server and print message from tcp client.
                Listen port 1234.
                Example : server .

con_test.c      It's test function Console Reader. Read and print message by
                console. Send command to console.  
                Example : con_test /dev/ttyUSB0 .

udp_client.c    It's test function Udp Client and print message from udp
                server.
                Example : udp_client server_ip server_port .

udp_server.c    It's test function Udp server and print message from udp
                client.
                Example : udp_server listen_port .

main.c          It's ALLIS main function.
                Include : 
                    configure.c     Get paramter from configure file.
                    serial.h        
                    socket.c        Tcp client socket function.
                    tcp_client.c    Tcp client soekct write/read function.
                    tcp_server.c    Tcp server socket function.
                    tcp_states.h
                    uart.c          Serial setting function.
                    udp.h
                    udp_mode.c      Udp server/cleint function.

                                        
serial.c        It's serial sample code.

 
